 which do not have primary enforcement responsibility)\\'94\\loch\\f0  is deleted.\r\n\\par \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 e.\\tab \\hich\\f0 40 CFR 142.308(a), 142.309(c). The phrase \\'93\\loch\\f0 the State, Administrator, or [the] public water system as directed by the St\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 \\hich\\f0 ate or Administrator\\'94\\loch\\f0 \r\n\\hich\\f0  is changed to \\'93\\loch\\f0 \\hich\\f0 the Department or the public water system, as determined by the Department.\\'94\r\n\\par \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 f.\\tab \\hich\\f0 40 CFR 142.308(b). The text of this subsection is replaced by the following: \\'93\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 At the time of proposal, the Department must publish a notice in the }{\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\ai\\af0 \r\n\\ltrch\\fcs0 \\i\\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 Arizona Administrative Register}{\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 \r\n or a newspaper or newspapers of wide circulation in the affected region of the State. This notice shall include the information listed in paragraph (c) of \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 \\hich\\f0 this section.\\'94\r\n\\par \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 g.\\tab \\hich\\f0 40 CFR 142.308(c)(7). The phrase \\'93\\loch\\f0 \\hich\\f0 the primacy agency\\'94\\loch\\f0 \\hich\\f0  is changed to \\'93\\loch\\f0 \\hich\\f0 the Department.\\'94\r\n\\par }\\pard\\plain \\ltrpar\\s62\\qj \\fi-360\\li720\\ri0\\sl200\\slmult0\\widctlpar\\tx720\\tx1080\\tx1440\\tx1800\\tx2160\\tx2520\\tx2880\\tx3240\\tx3600\\tx3960\\tx4320\\tx4680\\wrapdefault\\faauto\\rin0\\lin720\\itap0 \\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0\\afs18\\alang1025 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \r\n\\fs18\\cf1\\lang1033\\langfe1033\\loch\\af0\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\charscalex0\\cgrid\\langnp1033\\langfenp1033 {\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 8. \\tab \\hich\\f0 \r\n