ex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 R18-4-105.01.}{\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\ab0\\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \r\n\\b0\\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\tab \\tab }{\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 Renumbered\r\n\\par }\\pard\\plain \\ltrpar\\s34\\qc \\li0\\ri0\\sb100\\sl200\\slmult0\\keepn\\widctlpar\\wrapdefault\\faauto\\rin0\\lin0\\itap0 \\rtlch\\fcs1 \\ab\\af0\\afs18\\alang1025 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \r\n\\b\\fs18\\cf1\\lang1033\\langfe1033\\loch\\af0\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\charscalex0\\cgrid\\langnp1033\\langfenp1033 {\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 Historical Note\r\n\\par }\\pard\\plain \\ltrpar\\s35\\qc \\fi-360\\li360\\ri360\\sa100\\sl200\\slmult0\\widctlpar\\wrapdefault\\faauto\\rin360\\lin360\\itap0 \\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0\\afs18\\alang1025 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \r\n\\fs18\\cf1\\lang1033\\langfe1033\\loch\\af0\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\charscalex0\\cgrid\\langnp1033\\langfenp1033 {\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 \r\nNew Section made by final rulemaking at 8 A.A.R. 3046, effective May \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 6, 2002 (Supp. 02-3). Section renumbered to R18-4-105 at 8 A.A.R. 2756, effective June 6, 2002 (Supp. 02-3).\r\n\\par }\\pard\\plain \\ltrpar\\s15\\qj \\li0\\ri0\\sb120\\sl200\\slmult0\\nowidctlpar\\tx1180\\wrapdefault\\faauto\\rin0\\lin0\\itap0 \\rtlch\\fcs1 \\ab\\af0\\afs18\\alang1025 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \r\n\\b\\fs18\\cf1\\lang1033\\langfe1033\\loch\\af0\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\charscalex0\\cgrid\\langnp1033\\langfenp1033 {\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 R18-4-106.\\tab Reporting and Recordkeeping \\hich\\f0 \r\n\\endash \\loch\\f0  40 CFR 141, Subpart D\r\n\\par }\\pard\\plain \\ltrpar\\s59\\qj \\fi-360\\li360\\ri0\\sl200\\slmult0\\widctlpar\\tx360\\tx720\\tx1080\\tx1440\\tx1800\\tx2160\\tx2520\\tx2880\\tx3240\\tx3600\\tx3960\\tx4320\\tx4680\\wrapdefault\\faauto\\rin0\\lin360\\itap0 \\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0\\afs18\\alang1025 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \r\n\\fs18\\cf1\\lang1033\\langfe1033\\loch\\af0\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\charscalex0\\cgrid\\langnp1033\\langfenp1033 {\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\ab\\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\b\\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 A.}{\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \r\n\\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\tab \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 40 CFR 141, Subpart D (40 CFR 141.31 through 141.35), is incorporated by referenc\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 \r\ne as of the date specified in R18-4-102; this incorporation does not include any later amendments or editions. The requirements in the following subsections are in addition to the requirements of 40 CFR 141, Subpart D.\r\n\\par }{\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\ab\\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\b\\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 B.}{\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\tab \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 Department reporting forms. A publ\r\n\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 ic water system shall report to the Department the results of all analyses completed under this Chapter on Department-approved forms.\r\n\\par }{\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\ab\\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\b\\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 C.}{\\rtlch\\fcs1 \\af0 \\ltrch\\fcs0 \\charscalex100\\insrsid12746246 \\tab \\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 \r\nDirect reporting. A public water system may contract with a laboratory or another agent to report monitoring results to\\hich\\af0\\dbch\\af31505\\loch\\f0 \r\n the Department, but the public water system remains legally responsible for compliance with reporting requirements.\r\n\\par }\\pard\\plain \\ltrpar\\s34\\qc \\li0\\ri0\\sb100\\sl200\\slmult0\\keepn\\widctlpar\\wrapdefault\\faauto\\rin0\\lin0\\itap0 \\rtlch\\fcs1 \\ab\\af0\\afs18\\alang1025 \